{
  "info": {
    "name": "STEEL E-Commerce API",
    "description": "Colección completa de la API REST de STEEL.\n\n## Configuración rápida\n1. Ejecutá **Login** para obtener el token JWT.\n2. El token y el userId se guardan automáticamente en las variables de colección.\n3. Todos los requests protegidos lo usan de forma automática.\n\n## Organización\nLos requests están agrupados por **rol requerido** y dentro de cada carpeta ordenados por verbo HTTP: GET → PATCH → POST → DELETE.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000/api/v1",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "userId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "productId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "productSlug",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "orderId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "🔓 Público · Auth",
      "description": "Endpoints de autenticación sin requerir token JWT.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Registrar usuario",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Juan\",\n  \"lastName\": \"Pérez\",\n  \"email\": \"juan@email.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Segura123!\",\n  \"confirmPassword\": \"Segura123!\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/sign-up",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "auth",
                "sign-up"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Crea una nueva cuenta de usuario. Rol por defecto: `[\"user\"]`. No requiere autenticación."
          },
          "response": [],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    const response = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('userId', response.data.id);",
                  "    pm.test('Usuario registrado correctamente', () => {",
                  "        pm.expect(response.status).to.equal('success');",
                  "        pm.expect(response.data).to.have.property('id');",
                  "    });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"juan@email.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Segura123!\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "auth",
                "login"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Autentica al usuario y devuelve un JWT en `data.token`. El refresh token se setea automáticamente como cookie `httpOnly` (no se devuelve en el body). El token y el userId se guardan automáticamente como variables de colección."
          },
          "response": [],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const response = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', response.data.token);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('userId', response.data.user.id);",
                  "    // El refreshToken llega SOLO como cookie httpOnly (no en el body)",
                  "    pm.test('Login exitoso — token guardado', () => {",
                  "        pm.expect(response.data.token).to.be.a('string');",
                  "        pm.expect(response.data.user).to.have.property('id');",
                  "    });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/logout",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "auth",
                "logout"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Cierra la sesión del usuario eliminando la cookie `refreshToken`. No requiere body ni Authorization header."
          },
          "response": [],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const response = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', '');",
                  "    pm.test('Logout exitoso — cookie eliminada', () => {",
                  "        pm.expect(response.status).to.equal('success');",
                  "    });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh Token",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "auth",
                "refresh"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Renueva el access token usando el refresh token almacenado en la cookie `httpOnly` (seteada automáticamente en el login).\n\n**No requiere body ni Authorization header.** El navegador/Postman envía la cookie automáticamente.\n\n**Flujo de rotación:**\n1. El servidor verifica el `refreshToken` de la cookie\n2. Genera un nuevo access token (2h) y un nuevo refresh token (7d)\n3. El nuevo refresh token se setea en la cookie (reemplaza el anterior)\n4. El nuevo access token se devuelve en `accessToken` del body\n\n**Errores:** `401` si no hay cookie, el token es inválido o ya expiró."
          },
          "response": [],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const response = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', response.accessToken);",
                  "    pm.test('Access token renovado correctamente', () => {",
                  "        pm.expect(response.status).to.equal('success');",
                  "        pm.expect(response.accessToken).to.be.a('string');",
                  "    });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "🔓 Público · Products",
      "description": "Consulta del catálogo de productos. No requiere autenticación.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar productos",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/products/?page=1&limit=12&sort=-price,name&search=tubo&category=acero&discount=true&featured=true&price[gte]=100&price[lte]=500&stock[gte]=10&stock[lte]=50",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "products",
                ""
              ],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "1", "disabled": true, "description": "Página (default: 1)" },
                { "key": "limit", "value": "12", "disabled": true, "description": "Cantidad por página (default: 12)" },
                { "key": "sort", "value": "-price,name", "disabled": true, "description": "Ordenamiento (ej: price, -price)" },
                { "key": "search", "value": "tubo", "disabled": true, "description": "Búsqueda parcial en nombre" },
                { "key": "category", "value": "acero", "disabled": true, "description": "Filtro exacto por categoría" },
                { "key": "discount", "value": "true", "disabled": true, "description": "Filtro exacto por descuento" },
                { "key": "featured", "value": "true", "disabled": true, "description": "Filtro exacto destacado" },
                { "key": "price[gte]", "value": "100", "disabled": true, "description": "Precio mayor o igual a" },
                { "key": "price[lte]", "value": "500", "disabled": true, "description": "Precio menor o igual a" },
                { "key": "stock[gte]", "value": "10", "disabled": true, "description": "Stock mayor o igual a" },
                { "key": "stock[lte]", "value": "50", "disabled": true, "description": "Stock menor o igual a" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Devuelve todos los productos del catálogo con soporte para filtros, paginación y búsqueda. No requiere autenticación."
          },
          "response": [],
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const response = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (response.data.products && response.data.products.length > 0) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('productId', response.data.products[0].id);",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('productSlug', response.data.products[0].slug);",
                  "    }",
                  "    pm.test('Catálogo obtenido correctamente', () => {",
                  "        pm.expect(response.status).to.equal('success');",
                  "        pm.expect(response.data.products).to.be.an('array');",
                  "    });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
